text: Dianne I. Primavera (born January 28, 1950) is an American politician. She became the 50th Lieutenant Governor of Colorado in 2019. She is a Democrat. She was the Colorado State Representative for the 33rd district from 2007 to 2011 and again from 2013 to 2017. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Lieutenant Governors of Colorado Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Denver Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
